00:00:00.600 --> 00:00:06.166
Welcome to the Introductory Tutorial for PhotoModeler Scanner's 
SmartMatch and Dense Surface Modeling.

00:00:06.166 --> 00:00:10.166
This tutorial shows how to create a dense surface model using 
SmartMatch automation and multi-view stereo.

