00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:39.266
There are two types of automated projects, coded targets and 
SmartMatch.
This tutorial covers the SmartMatch technique. 

00:01:39.733 --> 00:01:43.733
Select the nine images used in the project.

00:01:46.800 --> 00:01:48.600
Hit 'Next' and a camera calibration prompt apears.

00:01:48.633 --> 00:01:50.699
Hit 'Next' and a camera calibration prompt apears.

